Ophelia Intensifies to Category 3 Hurricane

-- B y   B r i a n   K .   S u l l i v a n
-- 
2011-09-30T14:42:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-30/ophelia-intensifies-to-category-3-hurricane.html
Ophelia grew to a Category 3
hurricane with top winds of 115 miles (185 kilometers) per hour,
 making it the third major hurricane of the 2011 Atlantic season
as it churns about 620 miles south-southeast of  Bermuda .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Brian K. Sullivan in Boston at 
 bsullivan10@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
